{"tid":2248387,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泰政府強力水柱鎮壓民眾！　Nichkhun、BamBam心痛聲援：暴力無用","createTime":"2020-10-18T14:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T15:54:46.000Z","uid":74065,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"737576ee05553caab3fbadfe21f13a1239079c7b","tid":2248387,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"由泰國學生發起，自2014年以來最大的社會運動，在15日引爆三個月來最激烈衝突，宣佈進入緊急狀態。泰國政府出動水車，以強力水柱驅趕抗議民眾，畫面令國際震驚。不少藝人表達聲援，呼籲政府停止使用暴力，包括KPOP中的「泰國王子」2PM成員Nichkhun和GOT7成員BamBam。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/465637/org/af63d624137a5ee1c9e1391d909431de.jpg/pEdqovAyI22sCbZrmQK9tzLVAh1grzrbbSBghG0gYIQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F465637%2Forg%2Faf63d624137a5ee1c9e1391d909431de.jpg%2FpEdqovAyI22sCbZrmQK9tzLVAh1grzrbbSBghG0gYIQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=712c4cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Nichkhun（左）和BamBam（右）都是出身泰國的KPOP偶像。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\nNichkhun和BamBam不僅是同間公司的師兄弟，更都是出身泰國的KPOP偶像，兩人在推特都有超過600萬粉絲追蹤，影響力驚人。Nichkhun和BamBam都在17日於推特發聲，譴責使用暴力，聲援此次泰國學運。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5210/d5210150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5210%2Fd5210150.jpg&h=32235323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泰國民眾反政府示威，遭警方以水柱驅逐。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\nNichkhun在推特表示：「無法對使用暴力袖手旁觀，暴力沒有任何好處，希望大家都安全，HOTTEST要照顧好自己。」BamBam也在推特表示：「暴力不能解決任何問題，請不要對公眾使用暴力。聽取群眾意見和尊重個人權利及自由，才是解決的開始，請大家照顧好自己。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5212/d5212588.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5212%2Fd5212588.jpg&h=953226bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Nichkhun和BamBam在推特譴責政府使用暴力，聲援泰國學運。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5212/d5212589.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5212%2Fd5212589.jpg&h=59982623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩人的發聲讓家鄉泰國的粉絲相當感動，希望透過他們的影響力，能讓更多人知道泰國人正在進行的抗爭和困境。此次學運主要有三大訴求，包括：解散國會、停止威脅人民和限制泰國王室權力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5210/d5210149.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5210%2Fd5210149.jpg&h=3a175c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泰國反政府示威，遭警方以水柱驅逐。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n在這波抗爭活動中，泰國政府除了出動警力以強力水柱攻擊抗爭民眾、並關閉大眾運輸系統讓民眾「無法到抗議地點」外，更以「非正式下令」的方式禁止媒體在抗爭現場直播，並遭捕數名在現場採訪的記者，此舉也因為侵害媒體新聞自由遭到外界撻伐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5209/d5209813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5209%2Fd5209813.jpg&h=73596ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泰國反政府示威，遭警方以水柱驅逐。（圖／路透）"},{"pid":"9b39fde4d2205da2455b68a5f46adb46ddaaabf1","tid":2248387,"uid":9328,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"香港偽人: 我是中國人!"},{"pid":"334e153b393a3a16403cfe40771f65546d39c7c9","tid":2248387,"uid":128102,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"我想問去大陸搵真銀既lisa有無咩發表？"},{"pid":"991f00b7ddac195d69699887b3709af400e39568","tid":2248387,"uid":21141,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"香港偽人：我支持香港警察 你們可以打我了"},{"pid":"a4a47c37067b759ffaebe826c2968f6b0752805c","tid":2248387,"uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"334e153b393a3a16403cfe40771f65546d39c7c9","tid":2248387,"uid":128102,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"我想問去大陸搵真銀既lisa有無咩發表？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"暫時只有武漢加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab803307acd11bba41191966d1d3f7a2638f693","tid":2248387,"uid":14144,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"點解nickkhuh變撚左條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse